": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Tomb of the Golems", "keywords": ["Tomb", "Golems", "GREE", "Egypt", "ToG"], "long_description": "Spectacular VR action adventure set in Egyptian ruins!\n \n-Be on your guard in 360\u00b0 angle and defeat the enemies!\n-Battle with huge enemy bosses!\n-Find secrets and solve gimmicks!\n\n\n\n\n-Contact\nIf you have any inquiries about the App, please first read and consent to the Privacy Policy below and contact us at jp-gi-vr-support@help.gree.net, stating the name of the game.\nhttp://vr.gree.net/ja/products/golems/privacy/\n\n\n\n\n* Please note that GREE will obtain your e-mail address and other personal information when accepting your inquiries. \n\n\n\n\n-Warnings\nPlease visit oculus.com/warnings for warnings before using the Gear VR.\n\n\n\n\n-Our Policy Regarding Children\nThis App is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are under 13, please do not send any information about yourself to us, including your name, address, telephone number or e-mail address.", "short_description": "Spectacular VR action adventure set in Egyptian ruins!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "214719186444393", "locale": "ja_JP", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Tomb of the Golems", "keywords": ["Tomb", "\u30b0\u30ea\u30fc", "\u30b4\u30fc\u30ec\u30e0", "\u30b7\u30c9\u30cb\u30fc", "ToG"], "long_description": "\u300e\u53e4\u4ee3\u30a8\u30b8\u30d7\u30c8\u306e\u907a\u8de1\u3092\u821e\u53f0\u306b\u3057\u305f\u3001VR\u30a2\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u30a2\u30c9\u30d9\u30f3\u30c1\u30e3\u30fc\u304c\u767b\u5834!\u300f\n \n\u63a2\u691c\u5bb6\u30b7\u30c9\u30cb\u30fc\u305f\u3061\u3068\u4e00\u7dd2\u306b\u3001\u8b0e\u306e\u795e\u6bbf\u304b\u3089\u306e\u8131\u51fa\u3092\u76ee\u6307\u305b!\n\n\n*360\u5ea6\u3001\u5168\u65b9\u5411\u304b\u3089\u8feb\u308b\u795e\u306e\u5316\u8eab\u305f\u3061\u3092\u